{"tid":273816,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Twins﹕無試過愛上同一個人","createTime":"2017-06-07T00:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T01:38:48.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30f0c6d888d85f9104230e83dbfedeaa7a976406","tid":273816,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:58:02.000Z","msg":"明報專訊】Twins蔡卓妍（阿Sa）、 鍾欣潼（阿嬌）昨聯同鄭希怡（Yumiko）、衛詩雅、盧巧音、J Arie及李敏出席《原諒他77次》閨密分享愛活動。阿Sa不知是電影宣傳活動，以為是跟年輕人的分享會。問Twins的愛情觀是什麼？阿Sa說：「他愛我、我愛他。」阿嬌表示與阿Sa的觀點一樣，但不會是同一個人，她們亦從未試愛上同一個人。<br />\n談到阿嬌發生艷照風波翌年，拍了一段由微笑到哭的短片《0.7%的鹽》，最近短片與7件作品在內地進行慈善拍賣，估計籌得280萬港元。阿嬌懵然不知，反問道﹕「拍賣？我有無得分。」身邊助手指是做慈善，無錢分的。問阿嬌當時是懷着什麼心情而哭？阿嬌說﹕「每個人喊的方法不一樣，我沒想什麼，想什麼更難喊，當時只盡全力投入去演。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170607/s00016/1496772210577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170607%2Fs00016%2F1496772210577&d=XXyqayngBpANlTYFuenLwPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=a6a5d38d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170607%2Fs00016%2F1496772210577&h=ab389009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170607/s00016/1496772210577</a><br />\n果然好姊妹"},{"pid":"84fde2484b026d8f3ad2dbf59a47b2fa6e3875a2","tid":273816,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"一個鐘意麻甩佬一個mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d8fbd9722228439c0bf20c7c98ea8c43f9535a","tid":273816,"uid":118551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"但唔係話無試過同同一個人做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87832c984bfc221ad137a48a0784829a11217baa","tid":273816,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但唔係話無試過同同一個人做愛<img src=\"/asset